# Path to your ESP-IDF installation (one line, no quotes).
# Copy to .idf_path and edit:  cp .idf_path.example .idf_path
#
# To find it: in a terminal where "idf.py" works, run:  dirname $(dirname $(which idf.py))
# Or check your ESP-IDF extension / installer (e.g. ~/.espressif, or the folder that contains export.sh).
#
# /path/to/esp-idf
